## Git Workflow

This project uses the Claude Code slash commands for Git workflow:

| Command        | Purpose                                      |
| -------------- | -------------------------------------------- |
| `/start`       | Create feature branch from ticket            |
| `/commit`      | Stage and commit with conventions            |
| `/finish`      | Create PR with comprehensive description     |
| `/release`     | Create release branch and PR to main         |
| `/release-notes` | Generate GitHub release notes              |
| `/sync`        | Back-merge main to development branch        |

### Branch Strategy

- **main**: Production-ready code
- **staging**: Integration/QA testing
- **feature/{ticket}-{description}**: Feature branches
- **fix/{ticket}-{description}**: Bug fix branches
- **release/{version}**: Release branches

### Commit Format

```
[Type] Message (TICKET-ID)
```

